OL,3,CNewly formed trust to protect Lough
OL,4,CNeagh
OL,6,FRiver associations based around Lough
OL,7,FNeagh are coming together to form a
OL,8,Fnew group which aims to conserve,
OL,9,Fprotect and enhance the waterways that
OL,10,Ffeed into Lough Neagh.
OL,12,FThe lough itself is the largest lake
OL,13,Fin the British isles and provides
OL,14,Faround 40% of Northern Ireland's
OL,15,Fdrinking water.
OL,17,FIt has made headlines for all of the
OL,18,Fwrong reasons over recent years due to
OL,19,Fthe appearance of a toxic sludge-like
OL,20,Fsubstance known as blue-green algae.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
