OL,6,FMultiple factors have resulted in the
OL,7,Fbacterial blooms.
OL,9,FJim Gregg has been carrying out what
OL,10,Fis known as a kick sampling test, or
OL,11,Fcitizen science test, on the Six Mile
OL,12,FWater for a decade.
OL,14,FIt involves wading across a stretch of
OL,15,Friver stream for around 3 minutes, and
OL,16,Fusing a fishing net to capture a
OL,17,Fsample of the insects and wildlife
OL,18,Fliving in the waterway.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
