OL,6,FHe told UTV it's important to sweep
OL,7,Facross the river bed floor to ensure
OL,8,F"you're covering different ground and
OL,9,Fthat you're cover a bigger area of the
OL,10,Friver.
OL,12,F"It's important that you do the same
OL,13,Fplace every time you come to a site so
OL,14,Fthat you get like for like.
OL,16,F"Certain sites will have more insects
OL,17,Fthat others, so it's important you try
OL,18,Fand get a consistent test at your
OL,19,Fsite," he added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
