OL,6,FOnce collected, the sample is then
OL,7,Fpoured onto a white tray where insect
OL,8,Fspecies can be easily identified,
OL,9,Fcounted and a rating provided.
OL,10,FTypically, the higher the number of
OL,11,Finsects and species found, the better
OL,12,Fthe water quality.
OL,14,FOn the day Jim carried out the test
OL,15,Fwith UTV he noted a score of eight.
OL,17,F"The trigger level is 5 or 6 so I'm
OL,18,Fwell happy with that," he explained.
