OL,6,FExpertise like Jim's are now being
OL,7,Fshared with other angling associations
OL,8,Faround the lough through the newly
OL,9,Fformed Lough Neagh Rivers Trust.
OL,11,F"The trust is essentially about
OL,12,Fbringing our knowledge together to
OL,13,Fimprove water quality in Lough Neagh,"
OL,14,Fsaid David Kennedy the trust's chief
OL,15,Fexecutive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
