OL,6,F"if we just have a singular focus on
OL,7,Fthe lough we miss the big issue and
OL,8,Fthat is that the rivers that bring all
OL,9,Fof the pollutants to the lough and we
OL,10,Fsee the result with the blue green
OL,11,Falgae and so, essentially, if you fix
OL,12,Fthe rivers then you fix the lough.
OL,14,FHe added: "We are there as a critical
OL,15,Ffriend (to the agriculture and
OL,16,Fenvironment minister and his
OL,17,Fdepartment).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
