OL,6,F"Where there is excellent work we'll
OL,7,Fsing about it from the roof tops,
OL,8,Fwhere there are things to be
OL,9,Fchallenged, we'll be working with the
OL,10,Fangling clubs along the water ways to
OL,11,Fbring that forward based on an
OL,12,Fevidence based approach, it's not just
OL,13,Fhowl at the moon.
OL,15,F"The real work has to start now
OL,16,Fbecause if it doesn't not we'll be
OL,17,Ftalking about this in another 10 and
OL,18,F20 years time."
